f78ac211-4527-49af-af0e-0f03535b8bc0.title: <player>
f78ac211-4527-49af-af0e-0f03535b8bc0.text: Hi there. What is this place?

315dcf28-a4d0-48dc-b734-ecb6d70d5000.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
315dcf28-a4d0-48dc-b734-ecb6d70d5000.text: Ah, this be the Tower of Life! Beautiful, isn't it?

896fd05c-e47c-4562-995a-d3e3c30c559a.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
896fd05c-e47c-4562-995a-d3e3c30c559a.text:
Simple. I like to turn things from one form into
another. You've heard of the principle of equal trade?

8c0b3f93-21a1-4d12-bded-0fd5e8117a10.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
8c0b3f93-21a1-4d12-bded-0fd5e8117a10.text:
No, no, no. As in everything is made of substance. You
simply have to know what ingredients you need and
how to combine them, then you can make anything,
though you can't make something from nothing.

78c65df2-815b-4bce-ae82-49118e558f22.title: <player>
78c65df2-815b-4bce-ae82-49118e558f22.text: Do you know where I can find Bonafido?

d8f30004-14ef-4981-81f0-19170613d33b.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
d8f30004-14ef-4981-81f0-19170613d33b.text: Well, the builder's hard hat MIGHT be a clue.

1d135a87-cb0e-4f88-ab22-638802d9b17a.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
1d135a87-cb0e-4f88-ab22-638802d9b17a.text: I question why you are so pleased about this.

e5793324-58fe-4990-8f5e-7c6841d37eff.title: <player>
e5793324-58fe-4990-8f5e-7c6841d37eff.text:
Well, I think it's a positive step in my career as a
courageous adventurer.

2e621374-85b4-4b1f-a8e4-75f5d9579d0a.title: <player>
2e621374-85b4-4b1f-a8e4-75f5d9579d0a.text:
I must say, the inside of the tower is really something
to behold.

590a1f1b-f019-40dc-ac61-e10440c8e885.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
590a1f1b-f019-40dc-ac61-e10440c8e885.text:
Why, thanks. You'll find various pieces of machinery to
fix in there. You can no doubt find the materials in
there, too.

206af097-4150-4ef2-9129-74d844707bd4.title: <player>
206af097-4150-4ef2-9129-74d844707bd4.text: I can't believe what you guys have done.

df48f747-b755-4706-a627-9901122627fe.title: <player>
df48f747-b755-4706-a627-9901122627fe.text: I'm off to talk to the Homunculus.

4a45535e-e89f-4d52-917b-8254a727ad71.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
4a45535e-e89f-4d52-917b-8254a727ad71.text:
Rather you than me. Can't say you look like you'll
make it out alive.

fbf28259-58d2-4243-bc03-8b85cbfc597b.title: <player>
fbf28259-58d2-4243-bc03-8b85cbfc597b.text:
Thanks for the support. How about saying something
encouraging.

3f333762-e26b-45fe-90e2-246ae1defc84.title: <player>
3f333762-e26b-45fe-90e2-246ae1defc84.text:
I don't know. How about 'You can do it!' or 'That
Homunculus is in for a surprise'.

aeb10641-3cd1-4285-a7d1-46290e48d773.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
aeb10641-3cd1-4285-a7d1-46290e48d773.text: So, you want me to lie?

78d8a342-80e0-4d83-9892-d6c2569258bd.title: <player>
78d8a342-80e0-4d83-9892-d6c2569258bd.text:
Well, I've sat down and had a good chat with the
Homunculus.
